@page "/demo"
<PageTitle>Live Demo - Blazam</PageTitle>
<MudContainer Class="pt-5">
    <MudText Typo=Typo.h4>Live Demo</MudText>

    <MudText>
        We've prepared a demo of the app connected to a sample Active Directory Domain. It's  fully
        functional but there are some considerations...
    </MudText>

    <MudContainer Class="ps-4">
        <UnorderedListItem>
            There are no computers in the sample domain, this would be expensive to replicate.
        </UnorderedListItem>
        <UnorderedListItem>
            For security reasons, setting changes are disabled and some information will be censored.
        </UnorderedListItem>
        <UnorderedListItem>
            Remember that this is still beta, there will be bugs.
        </UnorderedListItem>
        <UnorderedListItem>
            Also, the web server and Active Directory/SQL servers are not on the same
            network, so it will be slower than in a proper environement. Plus it's a free web host.
        </UnorderedListItem>
    </MudContainer>
    <MudButton Variant=Variant.Filled Color=Color.Primary Href="https://blazam.azurewebsites.net">
        Go to demo
    </MudButton>
    @*<iframe style="width:100%;height:85%" src="https://blazam.azurewebsites.net" />*@
    <DisplayAd />
</MudContainer>